Day one festivities: Tour De Yosemite 2023 🌳🚴🏻‍♀️ 

We got into the Valley around 3 AM, slept in the truck until the sun came up, walked to base camp for some ☕️, and then straight to the bike rental shop. Such a fun adventure and not having to deal with all of the traffic was a bonus! I would highly recommend renting a bike next time you’re visiting Yosemite Valley. 💚

Bike Rental ℹ️ You can rent bikes at two locations, The Yosemite Lodge Bike Stand located near the pool at Yosemite Lodge and at the Curry Village Bike Stand located at the Curry Village Recreation Center. Rentals are first-come, first-served basis. Prices: $30 Half Day / $40 Full Day @yosemitenps
